Name: TFZ-02
SkillDesc[1]: Hetero Deconstruct Unit, Hetero Repair Unit, Hetero Fire Unit, Hetero Explore Unit

Name: TFZ-03
SkillDesc[1]: There are two roads leading to the Boss.
SkillDesc[2]: All members take the same path. Defeat all enemies on the path to reach the Boss.
SkillDesc[3]: If you decide to split up, you can only reach the Boss after defeating all the enemies, except the case when all the members on one of the paths have fallen.
SkillDesc[4]: The Boss will devour all the remaining enemies to enhance itself.
